{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"🎵\n      Sponsored Question Packs\n    \n    \n      Brand-Native Content\n      Brands like Spotify, Netflix, Nike, or Airbnb sponsor themed question packs. \"What song are you right now?\" powered by Spotify. \"If you could go anywhere together?\" powered by Airbnb.\n      \n        Revenue model\n        Brands pay per pack activation or per completed response\n        Brand fit\n        High — lifestyle brands that want to be part of real friendships\n        User experience\n        Feels like curated content, not ads. Never interrupts the loop.","choice":"A","id":null,"timestamp":1775325377680}
